        {"name": "Fixes and new features in the Exploratory browser",
         "description": " The four datasets (Tropenmuseum, KB news bulletins, Amsterdam Museum and OpenImages) in the new version remain unchanged with respect to previous versions of the exploratory browser. Changes include updated event labels for the news bulletins, based on extraction work by Kim Bosman. Additional events have been extracted for the Tropenmuseum data based on work by Victor Kramer. Furthermore, provenance and license information has been added for media objects as well as for metadata triples (named graphs).  Filtering in the DIVE browser has been improved. Note: the integration of this browser in the linked data/tools workflow of the Media Suite will be included in Version 3 and 4."}
